 24\t- `PhotoController` (`/api/v1/users/me/photos`)\n    25\t  - `POST /api/v1/
users/me/photos` - 添加相册照片\n    26\t  - `PATCH /api/v1/users/me/photos/reor
der` - 重排相册照片\n    27\t  - `DELETE /api/v1/users/me/photos/:id` - 软删除照
片\n    28\t\n    29\t- `OssController` (`/api/v1/oss`)\n    30\t  - `POST /api/
v1/oss/upload-url` - 获取 OSS 预签名上传 URL\n    31\t\n    32\t### 核心服务\n  
